text: Pinós is a village and municipality in Catalonia, Spain. Pinos may also refer to: * El Pinós or Pinoso, a town near the Alicante/Murcia border, Spain * Mount Pinos, a mountain in California, US * Isla de Pinos, former name of the Cuban island Isla de la Juventud ** Battle of Pinos, a naval engagement ==See also== * Jorge Pinos (born 1989), Ecuadorian footballer * Los Pinos (disambiguation) * Pino (disambiguation) *
